text: Marisol Castillo Aragones-Sampelo (born Marisol Castillo Aragones; November 6, 1977) is a Filipino politician. She serves as the representatives of Laguna 3rd district since 2013. Before entering politics, she was a news presenter for ABS-CBN from 1998 to 2012. ==Political career== In May 2025 she was proclaimed as the governor-elect of Laguna along with Vice governor-elect JM Carait and against her opponents for the governatorial race Dan Fernandez and Ruth Mariano-Hernandez. ==Related page== * Peewee Perez - tag team partner for vice governatorial. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino journalists Category:Politicians from Calabarzon Category:People from Laguna (province)
